item.title: Toby Turner & Tobuscus - I Can Swing My Sword!
item.description:
I Can Swing My Sword! (Minecraft Song) by Toby Turner. It uses these Boomwhacker Notes: C, D, E, F, G, A, and an optional C-sharp. It does not use B from the diatonic set.
To see the Tobuscus animation video click here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eN7dYDYfvVg .
If you found this video useful please subscribe. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
